#PATH_ODES="../../ODEProblems/"
#@nbinclude(string(PATH_ODES,"J2_Problem.ipynb"));

function Energy(u,p)
     = p[1]
    R = p[2]
     = p[3]
    q = u[1:3]
    v = u[4:6]
    r = norm(q)
    v2 = dot(v,v)
    sinth2 = (u[3]/r)^2
    aux = (R/r)^2
    return 0.5*v2 - /r * (1 + 0.5**aux * (1 - 3*sinth2))
end

function J2ODE!(du,u,p,t)
    
     = p[1]
    R = p[2]
     = p[3]
    x = u[1]
    y = u[2]
    z = u[3]
    du[1] = u[4]
    du[2] = u[5]
    du[3] = u[6]
    r2 = x^2+y^2+z^2
    r = sqrt(r2)
    aux1 = -/(r*r2)
    F = 1.5 - 7.5*(z/r)^2
    G =  3 + F
    aux2 = *(R/r)^2
    aux3 = aux1*(1+aux2*F)
    aux4 = aux1*(1+aux2*G)
    du[4]=aux3*x
    du[5]=aux3*y
    du[6]=aux4*z
    return nothing
    
end
